  - var mainText1 = "Do you have dirty ducts or suspect you do? When you look at the duct above you, do you see elements of dust and debris gently moving in the wind? Then you need professional duct cleaning services from our company."
  - var mainText2 = "We have been offering our extensive HVAC system repairs and services for several years, and that includes duct cleaning. If you are looking for a duct cleaner that is thorough and ready to do the best job in the industry, give us a call."

