  - var ourService2 = "Duct Cleaning"
  - var ourService3 = "Duct Repair"

  - var leftClass = "dc"
  
  - var ourText1 = "Just because the air quality is bad in one room, doesn't mean you need a complete duct cleaning of your entire system. We can save you a lot of time and money by identifying and isolating the problem in your home without cleaning the whole thing and asking question later."
  - var ourText2 = "Next, we will begin cleaning the ducts. The first step involves scraping off any debris or materials that have clung to the sides of the wall. From there we will scrub with a hot solution to clear out all of the possible bacteria and fungus that might begin to grow, before finishing it off with a buff and polish."
